<blockquote>其實係咪所以尖子都去哂讀醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實尖子讀醫唔係正常？<br />\n<br />\n正路應該係想讀醫先會出力考 出力考先會做到尖子<br />\n<br />\n尖子去晒讀醫先係正常 反而唔係想讀醫但又做埋尖子嗰啲先係值得去諗箇中嘅原因<br />\n<br />\n例如之前有個超水級狀元入socsci咁你aim科廿幾分嘅科但就努力到考七科5**返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a0f38d7778deafecc6a0ea7916ac96b21a776f","tid":349883,"uid":66779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無尖子讀商科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHKU IBGM 勁多 6 柒狀元揀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIBGM真係為kong u個名嘅人先會揀 應該本身有晒人脈唔使靠faculty 自己讀緊FBE都不得不話佢廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2063a9e68f5833d3176b59969c5b2288cb12438a","tid":349883,"uid":69429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T00:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實係咪所以尖子都去哂讀醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實尖子讀醫唔係正常？<br />\n<br />\n正路應該係想讀醫先會出力考 出力考先會做到尖子<br />\n<br />\n尖子去晒讀醫先係正常 反而唔係想讀醫但又做埋尖子嗰啲先係值得去諗箇中嘅原因<br />\n<br />\n例如之前有個超水級狀元入socsci咁你aim科廿幾分嘅科但就努力到考七科5**返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都on9 唔通明明考到35分 因為想讀嗰科收30所以hea考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都讀醫 唔通個個都讀醫咩?"}]}